#: ../../source/workflows/drivers.rst:252
msgid "For data sources, more is generally better. Select all Landsat options for a consistent mosaic. If you like, Sentinel-2 can be added for more data, but as the tiling system of the 2 sensors are different you will be forced to use all available images - the option to select images will not be available."
